<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="most-adv">most <strong><em>adv</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /məʊst/    美 /moʊst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>最：</strong></h4>
<p>反 least </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Green is said to be the most restful color. 
据说绿色是最令人放松的颜色。</p><footer>2012 安徽</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>很；非常：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was most surprised to hear of your engagement. 
听说你订婚了，我特别惊讶。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="most-of-all">most of all</h3>
<p>1.<strong>最重要的是；特别：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Why don’t you just take the plane? It’s much faster. 
你为什么不乘飞机？那样会快得多。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Most of all, I don’t have enough money. 
最主要是因为我没有足够的钱。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The children loved their day trip, and they enjoyed the horse ride <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (much).  （2009 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. most  </p></div>